FT  29 AUG 92 / Markets: At a Glance - Smaller companies index falls
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The fall in smaller company shares accelerated this week. The County smaller
Companies Index fell 2.1 per cent to 798.71 over the seven days to August
27; the Hoare Govett Index (capital gains version) also fell 2.1 per cent to
1004.73 over the same period. The indices have fallen by around 23 per cent
over the last three months.
