<HEADLINE>
FT  29 AUG 92 / Markets: At a Glance - M &amp; G launches income PEP
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Fund management group M &amp; G is offering a monthly income personal equity
plan, based on six of its unit trusts. By investing Pounds 6,000 in the
Dividend, High Income, European Dividend, Equity Income, Extra Yield and
Midland &amp; General trusts, M &amp; G estimates plan holders will receive an
initial annual tax-free income of Pounds 418. There is the risk, of course,
capital loss. Investors will pay the normal unit trust initial charge of 5
per cent and the annual charge of 0.75 to 1 per cent; there are no
additional charges for the PEP itself. The minimum investment per fund is
Pounds 500.
